107тЖТ/**
108тЖТ * Converts this [CompletionStage] to an instance of [Deferred].
109тЖТ *
110тЖТ * The [CompletableFuture] that corresponds to this [CompletionStage] (see [CompletionStage.toCompletableFuture])
111тЖТ * is cancelled when the resulting deferred is cancelled.
